  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You have started to develop Medicine beyond other skills, delving deeper into its possibilities.</p><p><strong>Core Feats</strong></p><ul><li>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.wYerMk6F1RZb0Fwt]{Battle Medicine}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.tnzZvaJ97t0N9g6y]{Godless Healing}</li></ul><p>Choose one Skill Path and gain that path's Trained feat.</p><p><strong>Available Skill Paths</strong></p><ul><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.7KENK9X4t685gDut]{Remedies (Medicine) Path - Trained}</strong>: You are especially adept at crafting alchemical and magical healing potions.</li><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.R9IYXOslNBhsUZqW]{Doctor Path - Trained}</strong>: You mastered the science of conventional medicine.</li><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.6PuIkHZ5qcNKhBu0]{Anatomist Path - Trained}</strong>: Your knowledge of the humanoid body is immense as is your drive to change it.</li><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.Hubev5EdycleCTBi]{Unconventional Treatment Path - Trained}</strong>: You are a strong advocate for alternative, esoteric treatments.</li></ul>",
      "gm": ""
    },
